node.text:
Check out @guacapp.savings to help you save money automatically as you spend. Set a goal, anything from paying down Credit Card Debt to taking the Vacation you haven’t been able to save for in the past. Available on iOS and Android!

node.text: @quentin.quarantino put together a fully vetted way to directly support the people seeking rescue in Afghanistan. If you can, please consider donating to the link in my bio. If you can’t afford to donate, please consider sharing.
